OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWelsh language: Parents    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fasked to record baby talk  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents have been asked to record the  
OL,6, way they speak to their babies in Welsh
OL,7, to help others learn the language.     
OL,9,F"Parentese" is a way of talking that is
OL,10,Fmore interesting to young children,    
OL,11,Fsuch as calling a dog a "woof".        
OL,13,FWelsh-medium nursery provider Mudiad   
OL,14,FMeithrin and the National Centre for   
OL,15,FLearning Welsh aim to create a         
OL,16,Fcollection of phrases and words.       
OL,18,FProf Enlli Thomas, education expert at 
OL,19,FBangor University, said it could have  
OL,20,Fwider implication for other languages. 
